# Global Git Ignore
# =================
#
# Patterns for files that should be ignored across all repositories.
# These are operating system artifacts, editor configuration, and personal
# tooling rather than project-specific ignores.


# Operating Systems
# -----------------
.AppleDouble
.DS_Store
.LSOverride
.Spotlight-V100/
.Trashes/

# Resource fork files created when macOS writes to filesystems that lack
# native support for extended attributes (e.g., FAT32, SMB shares).
._*
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
Desktop.ini


# Editors
# -------
*.sublime-workspace
*.swo
*.swp
*~
.idea/
.obsidian/
.vscode/
.zed/


# Logs
# ----
*.log


# Assistants
# ----------
#
# AI coding assistants store context and configuration in these locations.
# They are user-specific and should not be committed.
.agents/
.claude/
.gemini/
AGENTS.md
CLAUDE.md
GEMINI.md

# Ephemera
# --------
.cache/
.local/
